Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 08 of Hand MRI
When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then Finding dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Soft tissue mass' from the dropdown menu
Then 'I describe' radio button is enabled and preselected
And 'I know' radio button is enabled
And 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Characterization I' tab is enabled and preselected
And 'Characterization II' tab is enabled
And 'Differential diagnosis' tab is enabled

And 'Palmar' radio button is enabled
And 'Dorsal' radio button is enabled
And 'Radial' radio button is enabled
And 'Ulnar' radio button is enabled

And a single selection localizer is enabled

And 'Size' input field is enabled

And 'Sharp' radio button is enabled
And 'Ill defined' radio button is enabled
And 'Homogeneous' radio button is enabled
And 'Heterogeneous' radio button is enabled

And 'Round' radio button is enabled
And 'Oval' radio button is enabled
And 'Lobulated' radio button is enabled
And 'Spindle-shaped' radio button is enabled
And 'Broad-based' radio button is enabled
And 'Stalked' radio button is enabled

When I click on the localizer
And I select any bone from the localizer
Then the selected bone turns red

When I enter a value between 1 and 150 in 'Size' input field
Then '2nd plane' input field is enabled

When I enter a value between 1 and 150 in '2nd plane' input field
Then '3rd plane' input field is enabled
